{"tid":642323,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[四月新番] 雷頓神秘偵探社～卡特莉的解謎事件簿～","createTime":"2018-04-25T16:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T12:22:19.000Z","uid":6752,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"78c302401e383932531cee24992fab8026a46e21","tid":642323,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DauwgWtVAAA6I_6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDauwgWtVAAA6I_6.jpg&h=ecb83d10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事敘述卡翠愛兒為了尋找突然失蹤的父親雷頓教授，開始在倫敦從事偵探工作，從尋找走失的寵物貓，到找出殺人事件的犯人等，不論大小案件她都會承接，並以異想天開的解謎手法來解決這些事件。在會說話的狗助手「夏洛」（但外人聽不到）的協助下，展開嶄新的解謎冒險。<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n    原作：LEVEL-5<br />\n    監督：滿仲勸<br />\n    製作：LIDENFILMS<br />\n    角色設計原案：長野拓造<br />\n    角色設計：高田謠子<br />\n    助監督：migmi<br />\n    道具設計：小野田貴之<br />\n    色彩設計：茂木孝浩<br />\n    美術監督：中久木孝將<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n    卡翠愛兒：花澤香菜<br />\n    夏洛：小杉十太郎<br />\n    諾亞&middot;蒙特爾：池田恭祐<br />\n    大吉嶺&middot;阿斯波洛警部：多田野曜平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOn air<br />\n日本地區時間<br />\n富士電視台 4月8日（星期日）早上 08:30 首播<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/anime_layton\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanime_layton&d=e%2BbPU5a5VNOom2vgjLfwyKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8cda4cdb\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/anime_layton</a><br />\n<br />\n香菜d演技好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db2f3b899534bdd4a8565579f8ca2635c90ca5b","tid":642323,"uid":32402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:44:45.000Z","msg":"係唔係同以前NDS個隻game有關？"},{"pid":"8e4e4a6c0738d1ab5eb8b51e1f1d25b1c3af894d","tid":642323,"uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:46:08.000Z","msg":"雷頓系列 期待<br />\n以前睇過劇場版 都好精彩"},{"pid":"5653cedc300cde7719216068c71480237f69df59","tid":642323,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8db2f3b899534bdd4a8565579f8ca26